# 🚗 ITRent - Car Rental Platform

ITRent is a web-based car rental system built with **ASP.NET Core MVC** and **Entity Framework Core**. Users can browse, book, and manage rental cars, while administrators can manage reservations and monitor user activity.

---

## 🌐 Live Preview

> _Coming soon..._

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **ASP.NET Core MVC**
- **Entity Framework Core (EF Core)**
- **Microsoft SQL Server / LocalDB**
- **ASP.NET Identity (Authentication & Authorization)**
- **Bootstrap 5**
- **Font Awesome**

---

## 📦 Features

- 🔐 User registration & login
- 🧑‍💼 Role-based access (Admin & User)
- 🚗 Browse and book cars
- 📅 Create and manage reservations
- ✅ Admins can approve/reject reservations
- 📜 Status tracking: Pending, Approved, Completed, Rejected
- 💬 User-friendly UI with responsive design

---

## 📂 Project Structure

entACar/ │ ├── Controllers/ # MVC Controllers (Cars, Reservations, Account) ├── Models/ # Entity models (Car, Reservation, User) ├── Views/ # Razor views │ ├── Cars/ │ ├── Reservations/ │ └── Shared/ ├── Data/ # DbContext and seed data ├── wwwroot/ # Static files (CSS, JS, images) ├── Program.cs # App entry point └── appsettings.json # Configuration (DB connection string, etc.)

